text: Jan Beneš (born 9 October 1971) is a Czech rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1971 births Category:Living people Category:Czech male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Czechoslovakia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
